  <brief_title>Effect of Zinc Carnosine on Intestinal Permeability in Healthy Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of Zinc Carnosine on Intestinal Permeability in Healthy Volunteers Taking Non-steroidal Anti-inflammatory Drugs (NSAIDs)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
