  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Aged 18-35 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Conditions known to alter intestinal permeability, eg previous bowel surgery, celiac
             disease

          -  Conditions where NSAIDs are contraindicated, eg asthma, renal failure, heart failure

          -  Diabetes

          -  Any other serious illness
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
